diards \u00abDheepan\u00bb som vant Gullpalmen i fjor.", "Selv om den utspiller seg i Algerie i perioden 1989-98, f\u00f8les \u00abLET THEM COME\u00bb (Nova 4 kl. 20.30) som en ubehagelig aktuell film om framveksten av muslimsk fundamentalisme. En god, men vond film om \u00e5 f\u00e5 frykt og vold tettere p\u00e5 en vanlig liten familie."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "11f403c1d6733fb113d5af68b847d345e18b4883b099b1f46f0972f142be3837"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-03-09T07:39:49.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Krig, konflikt og terror p\u00e5 lerretet, kan gi film til \u00e5 bli litt klokere av."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/kultur/article12254047.ece/pqxnwp/ALTERNATES/w980-default/let_them_come.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/27018b9cb6eda7f8f3094f46d387fa2619e07111.jpg?5910b279"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "I terrorens tid -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "27018b9cb6eda7f8f3094f46d387fa2619e07111"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["Film", "Kosmorama", "Krigsfilm", "Terror"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Film,Kosmorama,Krigsfilm,Terror"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "arts-and-entertainment"}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": "nova 1"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": "film"}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["nova 4", "c\u00e9sar", "gullpalmen", "audiards", "nova 2", "dheepan"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["marseilles", "lyon", "cannes", "algerie"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["jacques audiard", "robert gu\u00e9diguian", "michel franco", "tim roth", "fatima elayoubi"]}, {"field": "kw-sentiment", "value": "negative"}, {"field": "kw-taxono